== Biography
Kai Wang is a postdoctoral researcher in the [https://www.lboro.ac.uk/departments/aae/research-and-innovation/ Department of Aeronautical and Automotive Engineering] at [https://www.lboro.ac.uk/ Loughborough University]. His research focuses on model predictive control, as well as robust and risk-based decision-making under uncertainty and constraints.\n
  
He received his B.E. in Space Information and Digital Technology from [https://en.xidian.edu.cn/ Xidian University] in 2017, and M.E. in Computer Science from 
[https://www.shanghaitech.edu.cn/eng/ Shanghaitech University] in 2020. From 2020 to 2024, he completed his Ph.D. from the [https://www.ntnu.edu/itk Department of Cybernetics Engineeering] at [https://www.ntnu.edu/ Norweigian University of Science and Technology (NTNU)].
